Metric Least Squares and Kruskals Non-Metric Scaling

Sammon

pacman::p_unload(dplyr)
## The following packages were not previously loaded:
## dplyr
library(MASS) 
loc2 <- sammon(dist(acidsamp), k=2)
## Initial stress        : 0.00139
## stress after  10 iters: 0.00068, magic = 0.500
## stress after  20 iters: 0.00067, magic = 0.500
x <- loc2$points[,1]
y <- loc2$points[,2]
plot(x, y, type = "n", xlab = "", ylab ="", main = "Sammon's metric")
text(x, y, olive[c(N, D, S), 1], cex = 1, col = cols)

### Kruskals non-metric

loc3 <- isoMDS(dist(acidsamp), k=2)
## initial  value 0.967788 
## final  value 0.967734 
## converged
x <- loc3$points[,1]
y <- loc3$points[,2]
plot(x, y, type = "n", xlab = "", ylab ="", main = "Kruskal's non-metric")
text(x, y, olive[c(N, D, S), 1], cex = 1, col = cols)

pacman::p_load(vegan)
proc12 <- procrustes(loc$points,loc2$points)

proc13 <- procrustes(loc3$points,loc$points)
plot(proc12)

plot(proc23)

plot(proc13)
